<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;">今天</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;">我们以“强国复兴有我，书写青春篇章”为主题</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;">向祖国深情告白</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;">对青春使命作出庄严承诺</span></p><p><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;"></span></p><p><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;为激发学生的爱国热情和民族自豪感，增强学生的责任感和使命感，引导学生树立正确的世界观、人生观和价值观，经济管理学院于2024年11月11日早上7:20在学校操场举行以“强国复兴有我，书写青春篇章”为主题的升旗仪式。本次升旗仪式由B220511班林雅婷主持。经济管理学院党总支书记蔡平出席本次升旗仪式，党总支组织委员、学工办主任、全体辅导员、各年级班长、团支书和其他班委、学生会所有成员、学生党员、入党积极分子、发展对象共同参加。</span></p><p style="text-align:center"><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20241111/1731331550393036650.png" title="1731331550393036650.png" alt="微信图片_20241111205624.png" width="640" height="329" style="width: 640px; height: 329px;"/></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><strong><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;">升国旗，奏国歌</span></strong></p><p><strong><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;"></span></strong></p><p><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;国旗护卫队迈着整齐的步伐护送国旗入场。在庄严的国歌声中，五星红旗冉冉升起，全体师生面向国旗，目光坚定，心中激荡着无尽的敬仰与自豪。</span></p><p style="text-align:center"><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20241111/1731331570468018833.png" title="1731331570468018833.png" alt="微信图片_20241111205630.png" width="649" height="415" style="width: 649px; height: 415px;"/></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><strong><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;">国旗下讲话</span></strong></p><p><strong><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;"></span></strong></p><p style="text-align: center;"><strong><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;">学生代表</span></strong></p><p style="text-align: center;"><strong><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;">B240501班黎素瑜发言</span></strong></p><p style="text-align: center;"><strong><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;"></span></strong></p><p><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;黎素瑜同学以真挚的情感，结合自身的学习与生活经历，倾诉着青年学子的爱国情怀与奋斗精神，让人感受到青春的力量与希望。</span></p><p style="text-align:center"><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20241111/1731331592662024626.png" title="1731331592662024626.png" alt="微信图片_20241111205635.png" width="658" height="437" style="width: 658px; height: 437px;"/></span></p><p><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;"></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><strong><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;">辅导员代表</span></strong></p><p style="text-align: center;"><strong><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;">陈娴老师上台讲话</span></strong></p><p><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px;">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;陈娴老师的讲话不仅极大地鼓舞了学子们，激发了他们勇于承担时代赋予的使命，同时也激励了他们为国家的繁荣富强贡献自己的青春和力量。</span></p><p style="text-align:center"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20241111/1731331614230083199.png" title="1731331614230083199.png" alt="微信图片_20241111205641.png" width="672" height="452" style="width: 672px; height: 452px;"/></span></p><p><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px;"></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><strong><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;">共唱《歌唱祖国》</span></strong></p><p><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 全体师生共同唱响《歌唱祖国》，歌声激昂，回荡在操场上空，表达着对祖国的热爱与祝福。每个人的脸上都洋溢着自豪和激情，用歌声传递着对祖国的深情厚谊。</span></p><p style="text-align:center"><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20241111/1731331629354094458.png" title="1731331629354094458.png" alt="微信图片_20241111205649.png" width="694" height="325" style="width: 694px; height: 325px;"/></span></p><p style="text-align:center"><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20241111/1731331645549080627.png" title="1731331645549080627.png" alt="微信图片_20241111205656.png" width="682" height="274" style="width: 682px; height: 274px;"/></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><strong><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;">总结发言</span></strong></p><p><strong><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;"></span></strong></p><p><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 经济管理学院党总支书记蔡平书记上台，为本次升旗仪式做总结发言。他鼓励学子们在今后的学习和生活中，要以实际行动践行“强国复兴有我”的誓言，让青春在奋斗中绽放光彩，让梦想在拼搏中成为现实。</span></p><p style="text-align:center"><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20241111/1731331680176076490.png" title="1731331680176076490.png" alt="微信图片_20241111205701.png" width="703" height="393" style="width: 703px; height: 393px;"/></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><strong><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;">合照留念</span></strong></p><p><strong><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;"></span></strong></p><p><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;升旗仪式圆满结束，全体师生有序前往主席台旁的阶梯，进行合影留念。这不仅记录了此刻的庄重与美好，更将成为同学们青春历程中一份珍贵的纪念。</span></p><p style="text-align:center"><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20241111/1731331695400038412.png" title="1731331695400038412.png" alt="微信图片_20241111205708.png" width="724" height="393" style="width: 724px; height: 393px;"/></span></p><p><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;"></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="text-wrap: nowrap; font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;">让我们</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="text-wrap: nowrap; font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;">以这次升旗仪式为起点</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="text-wrap: nowrap; font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;">将爱国之情转化为报国之行</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="text-wrap: nowrap; font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;">用实际行动共同书写属于我们的青春篇章</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="text-wrap: nowrap; font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;">让我们</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="text-wrap: nowrap; font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;">携手并进</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="text-wrap: nowrap; font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;">在强国复兴的征程中</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="text-wrap: nowrap; font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;">绽放最耀眼的光芒</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="text-wrap: nowrap; font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;"><br/></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="text-wrap: nowrap; font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;"><br/></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="text-wrap: nowrap; font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;"><br/></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><br/></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;"><br/></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><br/></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;"><strong><br/></strong><br/></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;"><br/></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;"><br/></span></p><p><br/></p>